  <brief_title>High Strong Ion Difference Fluid vs Hartmann's Solution on Acid-Base Status in Sepsis</brief_title>
  <acronym>HiSIDSS</acronym>
  <official_title>A Double-Blind, Randomized Control Trial of Rapidly Infused High Strong Ion Difference Fluid Versus Hartmann's Solution on Acid-Base Status in Sepsis and Septic Shock Patients in the Emergency Department Hospital Pulau Pinang</official_title>
